body:
@SsnL I've tried this using the binary build. So I think this is not the same as #6873, but may be related to a [problem](https://discuss.pytorch.org/t/rookie-not-getting-the-lstm-sine-time-sequence-example-to-work/16840) reported in the forum. 
@ylxie Could you please do the following things to locate the problem?
Change the flag `/Z7` in `setup.py` and `tools/build_pytorch_libs.bat` into `/ZI` and build again. And then, try to capture the error using some JIT debuggers like Visual Studio.
